parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the door to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to enter or exit the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The door will not unlock from the inside or outside
the door locks will not respond to the key or keyless entry
the door will lock and unlock intermittently
the door will not open from the inside or outside
and the driver may become trapped inside the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to lock or unlock unexpectedly, making it difficult or impossible to enter or exit the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The doors lock or unlock unexpectedly
the doors will not unlock with the key or keyless entry
the doors will not open from the inside or outside
the doors lock and unlock in a loop
the alarm system activates on its own.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving
the engine RPM drops to zero
the vehicle will not restart
the electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock/unlock mechanism can cause the door to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to exit or enter the vehicle, which can lead to safety concerns, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: The door will not open from the inside or outside
the door lock/unlock mechanism fails to function
the door becomes stuck
and the driver or passenger may become trapped inside the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the frame can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Cracks in the front frame
loud sounds from the vehicle
and failure of the vehicle's structure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tire can cause loss of control, accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Tire blowout
loss of control
and damage to the vehicle.
